    "However, the defensive measures in real-world AI agent scenarios have not been widely applied yet, and their performance remains questionable.To address these concerns from the root, it is essential to implement rigorous ethical guidelines and oversight mechanisms that ensure the responsible use of simulated environments in AI agents.",
